data.description: Charming Raised Ranch home in a nice established Blue Springs neighborhood! This is a very open and bright layout with many features! The main level features vaulted ceilings in the living room, gorgeous hardwood floors that flow throughout the main level, and a convenient laundry room just off of the large eat in kitchen. The basement offers finished flex space currently used as a possible 4th bedroom with a large closet, full bath and it walks out to the backyard. HVAC is only around 12 months old! Newer fridge, range, dishwasher and microwave! This home has the potential to move quickly with it’s large yard and nice view of the community lake from the deck! ***Note this home needs a little TLC to make it the perfect home!
